events.name: Temple Owls at Wake Forest Demon Deacons

notes.headline: MILITARY BOWL PRESENTED BY NORTHROP GRUMMAN

headlines.description: Wake Forest attached a positive ending to a season marred by scandal, using a strong performance by quarterback John Wolford to beat heavily favored Temple 34-26 on Tuesday in the Military Bowl.

video.headline: Wake Forest rides strong first half to Military Bowl win

headlines.shortLinkText: Wake Forest survives Temple rally to win Military Bowl 34-26

events.name: Army Black Knights at North Texas Mean Green

headlines.description: Jordan Asberry ran for a 3-yard touchdown on fourth down in overtime, sending Army past North Texas 38-31 on Tuesday in a rematch at the Heart of Dallas Bowl.
headlines.shortLinkText: Army rushes past North Texas in OT at Heart of Dallas Bowl

headlines.shortLinkText: Minnesota emerges from turmoil to upset WSU in Holiday Bowl

events.name: Boise State Broncos at Baylor Bears

headlines.description: KD Cannon had 14 catches for a Cactus Bowl-record 226 yards and two touchdowns, helping Baylor end a difficult season with a 31-12 victory over Boise State on Tuesday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Baylor rolls over Boise State 31-12 at Cactus Bowl
